channel.title: Whats up with this Dbow (Delta)
channel.description: My dbow is just hitting zeros and not losing any arrows....it shoots like a reg bow, yet nothing...the special hits on the dbow. Whats up with this dbow? I looked up the magic shortbow id and posted the dbow where ever that id is in my source, yet nothing How I fix this?
